ap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-j-hope-miguel-team-up-new-single-sweet-dreams-3844347"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-j-hope-to-release-two-more-solo-singles-this-year-3845540"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-j-hope-miguel-team-up-new-single-sweet-dreams-3844347"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p> <em>NME的</em>Rhian Daly在对J-Hope在首尔举行的开球演出的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/j-hope-bts-seoul-hope-on-the-stage-live-review-3842964">五星级评论</a>中写道：“很明显，他错过了舞台，这是J-Hope闪耀最聪明的地方 - 他对BTS显而易见，但现在他自己以自己的多面师师师和更强大地燃烧的是他自己更加强大的。”</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-j-hope-mona-lisa-single-3846730">BTS邮报的J-Hope发布了新单曲“ Mona Lisa”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
鲍比·威尔（Bobby Weir）公开对感恩的死者的“可能性”统治60周年https://www.nme.com/news/music/bobby-weir-open-to-possibility-of-grateful-dead-reuniting-reuniting-aas-a-trio-for-for-60th-Anniversary-3848071?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = bobby-weir-open-open-to-possibily grateful en grateful dead-reuniting-as-a as-a-trio-trio-trio-for-tor-tor-tor-60th nansiversarySurej Singh Fri, 21 Mar 2025 04:22:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsPsychedeliaRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3848071 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>感恩的死者去年年底透露，他们正在计划在菲尔·莱什（Phil Lesh）逝世之前的聚会</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bobby-weir-open-to-possibility-of-grateful-dead-reuniting-as-a-trio-for-60th-anniversary-3848071">鲍比·威尔（Bobby Weir）的邮政对感恩之死的“可能性”持开放态度，作为三人组成立60周年的“可能性”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/bobby-weir-grateful-dead@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grateful-dead">感恩之死</a>的鲍比·威尔（Bobby Weir）透露，他对乐队成立60周年的三人团聚的“可能性”开放。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/john-lydon-daft-punk-wanted-to-work-with-me-a-while-back-but-i-didnt-feel-the-vibe-3834722">约翰·莱顿（John Lydon）：“ Daft Punk想不久就和我一起工作，但我没有感觉到氛围”</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年，感恩的死者将庆祝他们成立60周年。早在11月，乐队透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grateful-dead-reveal-they-had-plans-for-60th-anniversary-reunion-prior-to-phil-leshs-passing-3816606">他们计划举行一次聚会的计划，其中有四个核心成员庆祝这一里程碑</a>，尽管由于共同创始人和贝斯手菲尔·里什（Phil Lesh）于10月，这突然被冰上了。</p><p>莱什（Lesh） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grateful-dead-bassist-and-co-founder-phil-lesh-dies-aged-84-3806464">于10月去世，享年84岁</a>。当时在社交媒体上分享的声明说，他“和平地通过”，“被他的家人包围着，充满了爱”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3806467" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806467" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806467" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1.jpg" alt="菲尔·莱什（Phil Lesh）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/phil-lesh-astrida-valigorsky-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806467" class="wp-caption-text">菲尔·莱什（Phil Lesh）。图片来源：Astrida Valigorskygetty</figcaption></figure><p>莱什（Lesh）逝世后不久，仍然是感恩的死者鲍比·威尔（Bobby Weir），比尔·克鲁兹曼（Bill Kreutzmann）和米奇·哈特（Mickey Hart）开头，开放了他们如何<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grateful-dead-reveal-they-had-plans-for-60th-anniversary-reunion-prior-to-phil-leshs-passing-3816606">考虑聚会，以庆祝今年与莱什（Lesh）庆祝乐队成立60周年，并定于排练时间</a>。</p><p>现在，威尔（Weir）在今年晚些时候在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/bobby-weir-grateful-dead-company-interview-1235290296/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队（Rolling Stone）</em></a>的采访时，在今年晚些时候没有莱什（Lesh）团聚而没有莱什（Lesh）的机会。威尔说：“我想当菲尔签出时，我认为这一想法也是如此，因为我们没有一个贝斯手已经与我们一起玩了60年了60年了。</p><p>但是，感恩的死去团聚可能仍然有希望，因为威尔还没有完全闭门，他们回来了。我们中的人可以团结一致。” </p><figure id="attachment_3833766" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833766" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833766" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dead_company_weir-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833766" class="wp-caption-text"> Dead＆Company的鲍勃·威尔（Bob Weir）于2025年的2025年年度音乐人在洛杉矶会议中心于2025年1月31日在洛杉矶会议中心。</figcaption></figure><p>在与<em>滚石</em>聊天的其他地方，威尔对他与Lesh的差异进行了反思，并回想起他们的最后一个电话：“我们确实有我们的差异。但是我从他那里得到的最后一个电话是，有消息传出，我们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-grateful-dead-members-honoured-by-us-president-joe-biden-there-are-still-a-lot-of-deadheads-around-3820275">在肯尼迪中心得到了荣誉</a>。他打电话给我只是为了给我和我们的全部理由，我们曾经打过我的理由，我一直在播出。我一直在召开。一点点，然后说：“好吧，在那里见。”</p><p>由于他们在12月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-grateful-dead-members-honoured-by-us-president-joe-biden-there-are-still-a-lot-of-deadheads-around-3820275">在美国总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）在肯尼迪中心（Kennedy Center）的表彰</a>，克鲁兹曼（Kreutzmann），哈特（Hart）和威尔（Weir）出席了会议。莱什（Lesh）由他的儿子格雷厄姆（Grahame）代表，而前主持人杰里·加西亚（Jerry Garcia）于1995年去世，由女儿特里克西·加西亚（Trixie Garcia）代表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3820284" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3820284" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3820284" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Bill-Kreutzmann-Bob-Weir-and-Mickey-Hart-of-The-Grateful-Dead-attend-the-47th-Kennedy-Center-Honors-at-The-Kennedy-Center.-CREDIT_-Paul-Morigi_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3820284" class="wp-caption-text"> Grateful Dead的Bill Kreutzmann，Bob Weir和Mickey Hart参加了肯尼迪中心第47届肯尼迪中心荣誉。图片来源：保罗·莫里吉（Paul Morigi）/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dead-company">Dead＆Company</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dead-company-announce-2025-residency-at-las-vegas-sphere-3819927">在拉斯维加斯球员场地开始了2025年的居住地</a>。</p><p>乐队是由Grateful Dead的Weir和Hart组成的乐队，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-mayer">John Mayer</a> ，Oteil Burbridge，Jeff Chimenti和Jay Lane  - 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dead-company-kick-off-epic-visual-feast-residency-at-las-vegas-sphere-3757420">去年取得了巨大成功的居留权</a>之后，他们回到了一个地点，看到他们在Sphere的240英尺240英尺屏幕前表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bobby-weir-open-to-possibility-of-grateful-dead-reuniting-as-a-trio-for-60th-anniversary-3848071">鲍比·威尔（Bobby Weir）的邮政对感恩之死的“可能性”持开放态度，作为三人组成立60周年的“可能性”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
